"text-xs text-olive-400 tracking-widest uppercase\">Olive Wisdom</p></div></div><p class=\"text-sm text-olive-300 leading-relaxed\">以科學與美學，精煉您的健康時光。<br/>為 35+ 知性人士打造的橄欖油科學與美學空間。</p></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-4\">專欄導覽</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-olive-300\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/?cat=culture\">知性史詩</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/?cat=science\">科學萃取</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/?cat=health\">品味鑑賞</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/?cat=lifestyle\">餐桌美學</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-4\">深度專題</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-olive-300\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/polyphenols-sirt1-longevity-2026/\">多酚與抗衰老</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/evoo-buying-guide-2026/\">EVOO 選購指南</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/mediterranean-diet-anti-aging-women-2026/\">地中海長壽飲食</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/hydroxytyrosol-brain-cognition-memory/\">羥基酪醇與大腦</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-4\">訂閱知橄週報</p><p class=\"text-sm text-olive-300 mb-3\">每週一封，精選最新橄欖油研究與生活美學靈感。</p><form class=\"flex gap-2\" action=\"/api/subscribe\" method=\"POST\"><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"您的電子郵件\" class=\"flex-1 text-sm bg-olive-800 border border-olive-600 text-white placeholder-olive-400 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-olive-400 min-w-0\" name=\"email\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"bg-gold-400 hover:bg-gold-500 text-olive-900 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">訂閱</button></form><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-400 mt-2\">訂閱即贈《橄欖油品飲師口袋手冊》PDF</p></div></div><div class=\"borde